\id PHM  - Mape NT [mlh] -Papua New Guinea 2008 (web -2014) 
\h Filemon 
\toc1 Filemonde Quraŋ 
\toc2 Filemon 
\toc3 Flm 
\mt1 Filemonde Quraŋ  
\mt2 Polji Filemonde Quraŋ ruaya.  
\imt1 Mimitaniŋ  
\ip Ŋi biŋeroroineke Filemon oi Kolosi sitio goku maŋine kerisieru zioz gio baku kiŋaŋqoqo tinaine Onesimus siŋaŋ gaya jibu kamiine useru Rom sitio raya. Oo raru Polke qojugaku buŋoine maneru maŋine kerisieru Polke Biŋe gio babire witi pigo rua yapebi ŋebu. Onesimusre damaŋ mataeme Polji Quraŋ yo Filemonde quraŋgaru Onesimusre meo ruaru soreme Kolosi kirieya. Quraŋ yoo maŋine kerisieya, ore biŋeine barariŋgaru Filemonde maŋ oi iŋi bapakareya: “Go kiŋaŋqoqogore baka bokeru iŋoke maŋmoakoŋ eru kepore tende maŋkekerisie ogogo oŋuine keririŋgoo dimako iŋore jerieru goigoŋ.”  
\iot Buk yoore mobe qoruine 4 oi iŋi:  
\io1 Buŋo fuŋfuŋgaine \ior 1-3\ior*  
\io1 Polji Filemon miteŋ gaga \ior 4-7\ior*  
\io1 Onesimusre Filemonde maŋ bapakareya \ior 8-22\ior*  
\io1 Qurande buŋo koruŋ qoruine \ior 23-25\ior*  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 O yoro ogone eru ogobabapine Filemon. Pol nonji Yesu Kristore gio baego ore eru nigiŋ nubi witi pigo ŋego. Maŋkekerisie ogone Timoti iŋoji noke ŋeko nonji goke buŋo mimane enimi ore quraŋ yo quraŋgago.   
\p
\v 2 Oŋuakoŋ ŋigo soguine maŋkekerisie seŋnoŋuŋ Apia eru Arkipus maŋkekerisiere mamari ŋinoŋuŋ eru maŋkekerisie kufufuŋ gore pigo tumaŋgaegobi, nonji ŋoŋore quraŋ yo quraŋgago.\x * \xo 1.2 \xt Kol 4.17\x*   
\p
\v 3 Anutu Mamanoŋuŋ eru Ofoŋ Yesu Kristo yokoji yauŋmoriri ŋarebire womoo goinebi.   
\s1 Filemonde maŋyauŋinere Ofoŋ miteŋ gaga.  
\p
\v 4 Nonji damaŋ so oŋga wosiru go manesu guego ore so Anutune daŋge yoore eru miku ojiego:  
\v 5 Go Ofoŋ Yesu manesiŋ garu manji jojoko eteru Anuture ŋiŋigo gbagbataeŋine sosowo manjoko eteru maŋyauŋ eyareru goge.   
\p
\v 6 Daŋge miku iŋi oŋga wosiego: Mamanesiŋgoji sanaŋgaru qaŋqaŋineke fukeko soine keririŋnoŋuŋgo dimaku niŋoke mamanesinde buŋo misaueku gomiŋ. Oŋu Kristoke qakatoru dimabeneŋ yauŋ fiine fiine noreega, go ore fuŋine sosowo mane sarigamiŋ.  
\v 7 O maŋkekerisie ogone, go ŋiŋigo gbagbataeŋine beufi qa yarende afagaru gogobi. Nonji manjokogo ore eru kokoine jeriebe oiji nonde maŋ kitiŋgaega.   
\s1 Filemonji Onesimus keporeiŋgo ore weuga.  
\p
\v 8 Goji oŋu goku Kristoke qakatokabere soine koimo fukeru usuŋ paiineo dimaku ya ruaiŋgo ore mitiga gorenobo.  
\v 9 Oi jibu Anutuji maŋineji jojoko enotega ore eru soine mimitine bokeru karieru weu garego. Go Pol nonde mosi manege. Nonji ŋi pogo fukego eru Kristo Yesure giore eru damaŋ yoo witi ŋi oŋuakoŋ fukego.   
\p
\v 10 Noŋ witi pi yoo ogogo tinaine Onesimus qotureru bapi gabe maŋine kerisieru mamanesinde madene fukeya. Ore eru muŋambe iŋore mi roru iŋore eru karieru weu garego.\x * \xo 1.10 \xt Kol 4.9\x*  
\v 11 Iŋoji rone kiŋaŋ qaku kosa gbedigaru rembeŋ goku qaqosori egareku goyayoŋ, damaŋ yoo qowirieru go eru noŋ fiine akoŋ bapi nopeko gioinere foriineji fukeeiŋgo so fukega.   
\p
\v 12 Iŋoji nakene yoro madene fukeme nakene yorone oŋuine sorebe kirieru goreo warega.  
\v 13 Nonji Bobiaŋ Biŋere eru witi pigo ŋego. Ore eru Onesimus kipeboŋ noke goku gore mobego bapi nuiŋ ore manego.  
\v 14 Oŋu manegoyoŋ, bapi nuiŋgo ore so bapakare gugo. Aŋigoji miko bapi nukande saganayoŋ, goji kiŋaŋqoqogo noremiŋ me sabaremiŋ, ore eru “Oŋ!” so minde nakekoŋ kipebemiŋ ore embimbiŋgago.   
\p
\v 15 Onesimusji iŋire eru boke guya me? Iŋoji damaŋ pompoŋine sakibe goku moke kirieru wareru goke damaŋ tatariine tomiri goiŋ.  
\v 16 Rone kiŋaŋqoqo omaine fukeru goyayoŋ, damaŋ yoo oi odureru ŋi fuŋine mo fukega. Maŋine kerisieru bio yoro ogonokuŋ fukega. Nonji iŋore aŋi kokoine manebe goji ŋi oi ŋonende Ofonde biŋe fukeko iŋore noŋ nadureru aŋi mokemoke yobu maneemiŋ.   
\p
\v 17 Goji noke oogo eru gogobere ore nonji warebe kepore nunoŋ ine, goji Onesimusji wareme oŋuine kepore teigoŋ.  
\v 18 Ya mo bosembea egoreya me iŋore tife mo goreo pega ine, oi nonde tife minde peine.  
\v 19 Noŋ Pol nake meneji iŋi quraŋgago, “Nonji oi bomukubemiŋ.” Nonji bapi gube maŋgo kerisiende tifego soguine oi bomukumiŋ ore gogake oŋuakoŋ nonde biŋe mimitari ende sagana. Ore eru soine iŋi minobo: Onesimusre tife oi minde gogakere tifego peine.  
\v 20 O maŋkekerisie ogone, Ofonde Biŋe gorebe, oi bokirieru bapi numiŋ ore aŋi manego. Kristoke qakatoge, ore so Onesimus keporende nonde manji afagaru fiaiŋ.   
\p
\v 21 Buŋone reŋ gamiŋ, oi manesiŋ garu buŋone quraŋgaru gore fuŋne iŋi peko manego: Buŋo migo, oi odureru fiine yobu eru sarigamiŋ. Oŋu.  
\v 22 Buŋo mo yo: Ŋoŋoji oŋga wosibi Ofonji noŋ sore nuku bokirie nume ŋoŋoreo wareiŋgo odigaru origago. Ore eru pi maŋine mo nonde bomogande ŋeine.   
\s1 Momojo eru mifia buŋo tatariine  
\p
\v 23 Ogone Epafras iŋoji Yesu Kristore giore eru noke witi pigo ŋeku momojoine ruame goreo foga.\x * \xo 1.23 \xt Kol 1.7; 4.12\x*  
\v 24 Ogopune gio moko baegobeneŋ Mak, Aristarkus, Demas eru Luk yoŋoji oŋuakoŋ momojoyaŋuŋ ruabi goreo foga.\x * \xo 1.24 \xt Apo 12.12, 25; 13.13; 15.37-39; 19.29; 27.2; Kol 4.10, 14; 2 Tim 4.10-11\x*   
\p
\v 25 Ofoŋ Yesu Kristore yauŋmoririji iiruŋaŋuŋ mifiagaru ŋoŋoke peine. Oŋu.   